  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released 07/05/2022 at 11:30pm CT</p><h3 id=\"id-1.18.8-Improvements\">Improvements</h3><ul><li><p>Improved how Date filters sort within all list view pages.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.18.8-BugFixes\">Bug Fixes</h3><ul><li><p>Worked through further Square refund issues, where after a pro rata refund would reflect correctly in Square but not in RepairQ.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>A problem preventing users from counting serialized inventory correctly has been fixed.</p></li><li><p>Internal orders now correctly recalculate open orders when rejected.</p></li><li><p>Disabling Square for one location no longer affects Square for all other locations.</p></li><li><p>Resolved a JavaScript error that would occur when using Qsite in specific scenarios.</p></li><li><p>Using the Supplier Sku column when exporting inventory no longer causes the exported file to come up blank.</p></li><li><p>The Devices List View now filters results correctly based on filters selected and applied by the user.</p></li><li><p>Resolved an error when users attempted to view Device History on a ticket.</p></li></ul>",
      "representation": "export_view",
